!Examples ii

Here the class `text-` e.g. `text-uppercase` is used to create callouts with text styling.

```
<<callout note src:"text-primary" class:"text-uppercase">>
```

<<callout note src:"A callout with uppercase text" class:"text-uppercase">>



!!Examples iii

Here `bg-transparent` class is used to create callouts with colored text and borders and no background.

```
<$macrocall $name="callout" type="info" src=<<.lorem>> class="bg-transparent text-info"/>
<$macrocall $name="callout" type="danger" src=<<.lorem>> class="bg-transparent"/>
```

